##Usage
To apply this component add class `rb-form` to the form element. If validation is needed add also attribute `data-module="validation"` and class `js-rb-life`.

Form element are placed inside container `form-field` and a corresponding modifier class is added to the container. For example when you use element `<select>` you
add class `is-select` the container `form-field`.
{{/markdown}}
